race.comment: KIWI MAKAVELI (7) impressed last time when produced a sharp 29.84 to finish second behind Last Splash in a new PB this course and distance. Expected to go close if runs up to latest. PUSH THE BUTTON (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (26.47) at Hobart. Form here sound including six wins. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Expecting another good run. BUCKLE UP TAJA (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Last Splash (30.22) in a Grade 4. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from six starts. Hard to beat again. BUNDABERG GUM (6) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.
